code: @Override protected TypeSerializer<?>[] getNestedSerializers(TupleSerializer<T> outerSerializer) {     return outerSerializer.getFieldSerializers(). }

@Override protected TupleSerializer<T> createOuterSerializerWithNestedSerializers(TypeSerializer<?>[] nestedSerializers) {     checkState(tupleClass != null, "tuple class can not be NULL").     return new TupleSerializer<>(tupleClass, nestedSerializers). }
@Override protected void writeOuterSnapshot(DataOutputView out) throws IOException {     checkState(tupleClass != null, "tuple class can not be NULL").     out.writeUTF(tupleClass.getName()). }

@Override protected void readOuterSnapshot(int readOuterSnapshotVersion, DataInputView in, ClassLoader userCodeClassLoader) throws IOException {     this.tupleClass = InstantiationUtil.resolveClassByName(in, userCodeClassLoader). }
